page: The Grim Adventures of Billy & Mandy
message: Well, I see no evidence that Billy and Mandy had seven seasons. So clearly, the show has SIX seasons. Just because the 2003 episodes WERE made for Grim and Evil DOES mean they count as season one episodes. If you don't think that, too bad. Also, season one came out on DVD in 2007, not 2004.
